<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <title>My Zoo Rescue Tracker</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: lightyellow;
      padding: 65px 30px 30px 30px;
      min-height: 1800px;
    }
    h1, h2 { color: darkorange; }

    .top-bar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      background-color: darkorange;
      color: white;
      padding: 14px 20px;
    }

    .list-item {
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid darkorange;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 5px 0;
    }

    .special-note {
      position: relative;
      left: 30px;
      background-color: gold;
      padding: 10px 20px;
    }

    .pet-card {
      position: relative;
      background-color: white;
      border: 3px solid darkorange;
      padding: 15px 25px;
    }

    .badge {
      position: absolute;
      top: 8px;
      right: 8px;
      background-color: forestgreen;
      color: white;
      padding: 4px 8px;
    }

    .section-label {
      position: sticky;
      top: 55px;
      background-color: darkorange;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      margin: 15px 0 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="top-bar">My Zoo Rescue Tracker - Simba the Lion</div>
  <h1>Meet Simba!</h1>

  <h2>Static</h2>
  <div class="list-item">Species: African Lion</div>
  <div class="list-item">Age: 4 years old</div>

  <h2>Relative</h2>
  <p>This note shifts right from its normal spot.</p>
  <div class="special-note">Rescue of the Month!</div>

  <h2>Absolute</h2>
  <p>The badge is pinned to the corner of the card.</p>
  <div class="pet-card">
    <p>Simba - African Lion, 4 years</p>
    <div class="badge">Healed!</div>
  </div>

  <h2>Sticky</h2>
  <p>Scroll down - the label locks at the top!</p>
  <div class="section-label">More Rescues Available</div>
  <div class="list-item">Luna - Snow Leopard, 1 year</div>
  <div class="list-item">Max - Grizzly Bear, 3 years</div>
  <div class="list-item">Daisy - Bald Eagle, 4 years</div>
  <div class="list-item">Rocky - Golden Jackal, 2 years</div>
  <div class="list-item">Bella - Border Wolf, 1 year</div>
  <div class="list-item">Charlie - Red Panda, 5 years</div>
  <div class="list-item">Coco - Siberian Tiger, 3 years</div>
  <div class="list-item">Milo - Cheetah Cub, 2 years</div>
</body>
</html>